{"tid":799693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀音坐蓮＋老漢推車＝老司機一家3口","createTime":"2018-08-30T09:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T09:44:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7140272693554319dcf679ac504cc95fbc2f5701","tid":799693,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180830/640_d3ff330780bc8f7d37e696d66c356ee7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180830%2F640_d3ff330780bc8f7d37e696d66c356ee7.jpg&h=3365c5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物盡其用！香港一名網友今天在臉書社團「巴打絲打 Facebook Club」分享照片，拍到一名坐著電動輪椅的殘障男子充分發揮輪椅功用，不但抱著妻子共乘，而且妻子還推著嬰兒車載小孩，2車3人8輪前行，畫面相當特別。<br />\n網友們看了紛紛留言「人形蜈蚣」、「老漢開車再推車」、「老漢電動推車」、「一山還有一山高」、「車推老漢老漢推姐姐推小孩」、「觀音坐蓮加老漢推車，同埋仙人指路」。也有網友分享另一張照片，在香港天水圍目擊一名坐著電動輪椅的男子抱著孫女，後方還載著女看護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180830/640_11d02120015db555993398d98c31dab4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180830%2F640_11d02120015db555993398d98c31dab4.jpg&h=b7cd33b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180830/640_1da5f5f624bfbed7f865fdf175b5347e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180830%2F640_1da5f5f624bfbed7f865fdf175b5347e.jpg&h=8aa03cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180830/1420897/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180830%2F1420897%2F&d=WSR0BhHqB%2BG9nNySSTDKzmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ffe4a3d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180830%2F1420897%2F&h=1b972376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/new/re